--- !u!114 &443461095
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 443461094}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b3084848c5897dd41b9239769188f1bd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: IRIS GABLE
  conversation:
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Hey, don't think we've met.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: I'm Iris. I have been doing photography for Max for four or four years
      now.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Did you know what he was announcing tonight?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: He said dress for a historic occasion. I thought it was another acquisition
      thing. Didn't see all of this coming.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: How are you feeling about it?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: I mean it is what it is. Clients come and go. It's just, Max is the
      reason I don't really have other clients.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: Four years of being basically on call for him, I never really built
      anything else up. And he knew that.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: You think he took advantage of that?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: I think Max likes having people who depend on him. Makes it easier.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: IRIS GABLE
    sentence: Anyway, I'm sure he'll be fine. Guys like Max are always fine.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: She seems a bit mad. I should leave her alone.
    isItalic: 1
  repeatLine:
    characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "She seems a bit mad. I should leave her alone.\r"
    isItalic: 1
  hasTalked: 0
